{"ProductId":"320","Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Chevron","ShortDescription":"Insulated faux wood garage doors with a classic chevron design","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/chevron.webp?sfvrsn=823f979a_21","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-chevron","Overview":"<h3>Chevron Style, Built to Last</h3><h4>Hardy 5-Layer Construction</h4><p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Chevron door features a tough, five-layer build&mdash;steel, insulation, steel, composite cladding, and a composite overlay&mdash;that delivers lasting strength and a premium finish.</p><h4>Genuine Wood Appeal</h4><p>Get the warmth and character of wood without the upkeep. The faux wood composite cladding and overlays are molded from real wood pieces, so you see every beautiful grain and texture.</p><h4>Signature Chevron Design</h4><p>Each cladding piece is precision-cut at a 45-degree angle, forming the bold chevron &ldquo;V&rdquo; pattern that sets this door apart. With 15 design variations and four unique patterns, you can make a statement that&rsquo;s all your own.</p><h4>Endless Customization</h4><p>Choose from Clear Cypress or Mahogany, available in ten standard finishes or over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg; custom paint colors</a>. Add optional windows and decorative hardware for a personalized touch.</p><h4>Superior Insulation</h4><p>2&rdquo; <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane foam</a> delivers an impressive 20.4 R-value, helping keep your garage more comfortable all year.</p><h4>Ready for Any Climate</h4><p>Ask about <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> for extra protection in high-wind areas.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Designed to Catch Your Eye</h3><p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Chevron garage door is crafted with a 5-layer construction that delivers both durability and standout curb appeal. At its core, a tough steel base provides strength and stability, while 2\" of <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane foam</a> insulation boosts energy efficiency with a remarkable 20.4 R-value, helping to keep your garage quieter and more comfortable.</p><p>On top of the steel, a second layer of steel adds extra resilience. The exterior features composite cladding and overlay, both molded from real wood to capture authentic grain patterns and natural texture. This advanced composite material resists moisture, rot, and cracking, so you get the classic look of wood without the maintenance headaches.</p><p>Corrosion-resistant hot-dipped galvanized steel skins, a baked-on primer, and topcoat ensure lasting protection from the elements. Additional safety features like patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg; and sturdy hardware complete the package, making this door as reliable as it is beautiful.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-canyon-ridge-chevron.webp?sfvrsn=3230860_5\" alt=\"Cutaway\" sf-size=\"6784\" /><ol><li>Composite Overlay</li><li>Composite Cladding</li><li>Steel</li><li>2\" Intellicore&reg; Polyurethane Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Canyon Ridge Chevron","DisplayIndex":2,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/canyon-ridge-chevron","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Chevron gives you a wide palette of finishes to perfectly complement your home&rsquo;s style and bring out the unique chevron pattern. Choose from warm, wood-inspired stains like Natural, Medium, Dark, or Walnut for a rich, authentic look that highlights the detailed grain of the composite cladding and overlay.</p><p>For a more contemporary vibe, Slate and Espresso finishes offer cool, sophisticated tones that work beautifully with modern exteriors.</p><p>Looking for something especially striking? Select models in Mahogany offer exclusive colors like Black, White, Bronze, and Charcoal for a bold, distinctive statement. If you&rsquo;re after a unique combination, the two-tone option lets you pick one color for the base steel layer and another for the composite overlay, creating a custom layered effect.</p><p>Prefer to start with a blank slate? Opt for the primed, no-finish door, ready for your own paint or stain. And if you want a truly personal touch, the <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">ColorBlast&reg; program</a> opens up more than 1,500 custom color possibilities&mdash;so you can match your door to virtually any color scheme.</p><p><em>*Available on select models.<br />Black, white, bronze and charcoal only available in Mahogany.<br />Two-tone option available. One color for the base layer (steel) and one color for the top layer (composite overlay).</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Chevron lets you customize the top section of your garage door to match your home&rsquo;s style and your personal taste. Whether you want arches to make it look more like a carriage house door or a row of crisp, square windows for a modern touch, the range of top section options makes it easy to personalize your door.</p><p>Choose from solid, non-window sections for a sleek, uninterrupted chevron look, or add windows for extra light and architectural interest. <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/garage-door-windows-guide\">Window configurations</a> include a wide variety of shapes and arrangements, from classic rectangular windows (like REC11, REC13, REC14) to square designs (SQ23, SQ24) and several arched options (ARCH1, ARCH3, ARCH4, ARCH13, ARCH14) for a more traditional or decorative feel. You can opt for single or multi-pane layouts and select from different top section patterns such as TOP11, TOP12, or TOP13, each offering a distinct look.</p>","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>Personalize your Canyon Ridge&reg; Chevron garage door with a range of hardware choices that blend functionality and style. Each door comes standard with spade lift handles&mdash;a classic, versatile option that suits almost any exterior. For a more customized look, upgrade to spear or colonial lift handles, or choose decorative lift handles to add a unique touch.</p><p>You can enhance your door&rsquo;s character with optional accents like the ring door knocker, escutcheon plates, or twisted \"L\" handles for a rustic, handcrafted feel. Step plates are available in spade, spear, or colonial designs, not only protecting your door but also adding a subtle decorative element.</p><p>Complete the look with matching strap hinges in spade, spear, or colonial styles&mdash;these can be both functional and decorative, giving your door the timeless charm of <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/garage-door-styles/carriage-house-garage-doors\">classic carriage house</a> hardware.</p>","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (5-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr5l-des11-rec13-tampa-showcase.webp?sfvrsn=d9bffbb6_1","Id":"30","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyonridge","DisplayIndex":3,"ShortDescription":"Insulated carriage house garage doors with faux wood composite cladding and overlays","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (5-Layer)"},{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (4-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr4l-d21-rec13-afp143r.webp?sfvrsn=8ae1d536_3","Id":"29","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-4-layer","DisplayIndex":4,"ShortDescription":"Stylish, low maintenance and insulated faux wood garage doors","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (4-Layer)"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-canyonridgebr-20-1.webp?sfvrsn=9c9dfc36_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-CANYONRIDGEBR-20.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Products Available Through Independent Dealers","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/idea-book.webp?sfvrsn=699cfb64_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-IMAGINE-14.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"Installation Manual for Residential Sectional Insulated Steel Doors","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/installation-instructions/installmanual-insulatedresi.webp?sfvrsn=15f3a601_3","Type":"Instruction Manual","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/INST-4150077_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Installation Warranty","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/warranty/cbpc-madadgdinstallwarranty1yr-15.webp?sfvrsn=99c1bfdc_4","Type":"Warranty","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/CBPC-MADADGDINSTALLWARRANTY1YR-15.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2},{"Title":"Canyon Ridge Care and Maintenance","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/care-and-mai